  </titlealts>
  <body>
  <div>
      <p>
An 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_integrated_care_system">Integrated Care System</xref>
 (<xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_integrated_care_system">ICS</xref>) is an integral part of 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_nhs_england">NHS England</xref>.        </p>
      <p>
An 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_integrated_care_system">Integrated Care System</xref>
 is a collaboration where NHS 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_organisation">ORGANISATIONS</xref>
 are in partnership with 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_local_authority">Local Authorities</xref>
 and other bodies, taking collective responsibility for managing resources, delivering NHS standards and improving the health of the population they serve.        </p>
      <p>
An 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_integrated_care_system">Integrated Care System</xref>
 is an evolvement of a 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_sustainability_and_transformation_partnership">Sustainability and Transformation Partnership</xref>
 to form a closer collaboration between the NHS and 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_local_authority">Local Authorities</xref>.        </p>
      <p>
For further information 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_integrated_care_system">Integrated Care Systems</xref>, see the 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_nhs_england">NHS England</xref>
 website at: 
              <xref href="https://www.england.nhs.uk/integratedcare/integrated-care-systems/"
               scope="external"
               format="html">Integrated care systems</xref>.        </p>
  </div>
